Equestrians and their steeds from different clubs in the province put their best foot forward during the fifth round of Western Mounted Games Limpopo qualifier at Winnfield Stables in Dalmada on Saturday.
They participated in different games such as the barrel race, speed ball, keyhole, poles 1 and figure 8 stakes. Supporters on the side-lines added some excitement to the challenge as they cheered on the riders.
The results of the competition were still being awaited by the time of going to print.
